org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.parquet.plain

Class ParquetDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.parquet.plain.ParquetDataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSource

    public class ParquetDataSource
extends Object
implements DataSource
    A graph data source for parquet files.

    The datasource expects files separated by vertices and edges, e.g. in the following directory structure:

    parquetRoot |- vertices.parquet # all vertex data |- edges.parquet # all edge data |- graphs.parquet # all graph head data
